filenamePattern.description: Target files whose names matches this regular expression.
lineLimit.description: Target this number of lines from head (if plus) or tail (if minus) of file.
birthTimeStart.description: Treat following of part that matches this regular expression as birth time field.
birthTimeEnd.description: Treat preceding of part that matches this regular expression as birth time field.
modifiedTimeStart.description: Treat following of part that matches this regular expression as modified time field.
modifiedTimeEnd.description: Treat preceding of part that matches this regular expression as modified time field.
momentFormat.description: Moment.js format string for birth time and modified time.
